works.description:
Photos that I have deleted are still  
appearing regarding Kerza Spires, a young child whose safety is a concern.
  
They keep appearing on google searches and I cannot find a way to have
them  
removed.  Someone has already copied and shared photos of her without  
consent and I do not know where else they can be.  Please help me in this 

matter as soon as possible.  Thank you.
